Description: Stunning Mixed Media Satchel !! Combination Suede and genuine Italian leather Guaranteed authentic Designer Claudia Firenze Made in Italy ~ New with tags Brand new, very chic Italian mixed media satchel. The front is constructed of brown suede and the back brown pebbled leather. The front features a large pocket with metallic gold snake skin print and turn-lock closure. The gold gives off an understated and subtle shimmer which matches beautifully with the rich brown color. The back features another large pocket with magnetic snap closure. The main compartment has zipper closure and there is a zip compartment on the inside back wall with a Firenze gold plaque of authenticity. The inside front wall has two slip pockets. The inside is lined with a matching brown fabric and there are four gold protective feet on the flat bottom. Dual rolled handles and gold hardware. This is a good size satchel, spacious enough to hold both a laptop and ipad. Great price for this lovely handmade bag! Approximate measurements: 17" wide x 14" high x 6" deep - strap drop 6" Please contact me if you have any questions or need additional pictures. Also please check out my other handbag listings.
